# IDE Control Surface Pack Implementation Plan

## Goal Description
Implement the "IDE Control Surface Pack" (Option A) to elevate the IDE from a preference-based environment to a normative control surface within the ADK. This pack forces alignment between local development and CI/CD pipelines, ensuring determinism and reducing "works on my machine" issues.

